message.content:
```json
{
  "endpoint_path": "/api/v3/swaps/{pool}",
  "description": "Get swaps for a specific Uniswap V3 pool",
  "method": "GET",
  "path_params": [
    {"name": "pool", "type": "String", "description": "The address of the Uniswap V3 pool"}
  ],
  "query_params": [
    {"name": "limit", "type": "u32", "default": 50},
    {"name": "startBlockTimestamp", "type": "Option<u64>", "default": "null"},
    {"name": "endBlockTimestamp", "type": "Option<u64>", "default": "null"},
    {"name": "offset", "type": "u32", "default": 0}
  ],
  "response_schema": {
    "name": "SwapResponse",
    "fields": [
      {"name": "block_number", "type": "i64", "description": "Block number where the swap occurred"},
      {"name": "block_timestamp", "type": "i64", "description": "Unix timestamp of the block"},
      {"name": "transaction_hash", "type": "String", "description": "Transaction hash of the swap"},
      {"name": "log_index", "type": "i32", "description": "Log index within the block"},
      {"name": "sender", "type": "String", "description": "Address of the swap sender"},
      {"name": "recipient", "type": "String", "description": "Address of the swap recipient"},
      {"name": "amount0", "type": "String", "description": "Amount of token0 swapped"},
      {"name": "amount1", "type": "String", "description": "Amount of token1 swapped"},
      {"name": "sqrt_price_x96", "type": "String", "description": "Square root of the price after the swap"},
      {"name": "liquidity", "type": "String", "description": "Liquidity after the swap"},
      {"name": "tick", "type": "i32", "description": "Tick at the time of swap"}
    ]
  },
  "sql_query": "SELECT block_number, block_timestamp, transaction_hash, log_index, sender, recipient, amount0::TEXT, amount1::TEXT, sqrt_price_x96::TEXT, liquidity::TEXT, tick FROM v3_pool_swaps WHERE recipient = $1 AND ($2::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp >= $2) AND ($3::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp <= $3) ORDER BY block_timestamp DESC LIMIT $4 OFFSET $5",
  "tables_referenced": ["v3_pool_swaps"]
}
```
